Eugene Byrd https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eugene_Byrd 0 Eugene Byrd (born August 28, 1975) is an American actor. Byrd was born and raised in Philadelphia, where he graduated from Greene Street Friends School in 1989 and The Crefeld School in 1993. He began acting as a child, appearing as Arthur in the movie My Little Girl in 1986. He is best known for his portrayal of Dr. Clark Edison on the series Bones.
